 <text>
  <front>
   <head>NAY, NAY, CENSOR TIME.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">NAY, nay, Censor Time, I'll be happy to-day,</l>
     <l n="2" met="--+|--+|--+" line_length="9">For I see thou'rt grown gray with thy cares;</l>
     <l n="3" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">Then preach not to me, as my life steals away,</l>
     <l n="4" met="--+|--+|--+" line_length="9">Of the pleasure of far distant years.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">The sands in thy glass in soft silence depart,</l>
     <l n="6" met="--+|--+|--+" line_length="9">Yet thy cheek grows the paler the while;</l>
     <l n="7" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">But the drops there in mine fill the tubes of the heart,</l>
     <l n="8" met="--+|--+|--+" line_length="9">And mount to my lip with a smile.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">And thou would'st smile too, if my fair one thou'd toast;</l>
     <l n="10" met="--+|--+|--+" line_length="9">Nay sip of my bumper and see!</l>
     <l n="11" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">Her charms will dissolve e'en thy age's chill frost,</l>
     <l n="12" met="--+|--+|--+" line_length="9">And make thee as youthful as me.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="4" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="13" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">To be young, cried old Time, my own glass I'll forego,</l>
     <l n="14" met="--+|--+|--+" line_length="9">And freely will sip out of thine;</l>
     <l n="15" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">Then tasted, and cried, Let thy Cynthia now know</l>
     <l n="16" met="--+|--+|--+" line_length="9">She has warm'd the cold bosom of Time.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="5" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="17" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">For this the late rose shall still hang on her cheek,</l>
     <l n="18" met="--+|--+|--+" line_length="9">Though the blossoms of youth should decay;</l>
     <l n="19" met="--+|--+|--+|--+" line_length="12">And the soft eye be left, its own language to speak,</l>
     <l n="20" met="--+|--+|--+" line_length="9">For a mind far more beauteous than they!</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
